{"type":"message","id":"28a77032","parentId":"662b9910","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:56:38.194Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_d7vco6fm6ow6_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4853\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=882\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\n[mutation proposed] a\n[master bf7eb8a] pulse: 2026-03-24 125614\n 5 files changed, 263 insertions(+), 124 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 125614.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 125614.mutation\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 125614 - The CFI Compression experiment revealed the need for a hybrid approach - pure CFI thresholds fail because constant-format tokens (freq=160, CFI=1.0) are metaprogramming artifacts, not meaningful patterns. The concrete scoring formula is now defined: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120).\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"delta-reef","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4853\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=882\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\n[mutation proposed] a\n[master bf7eb8a] pulse: 2026-03-24 125614\n 5 files changed, 263 insertions(+), 124 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 125614.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 125614.mutation\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 125614 - The CFI Compression experiment revealed the need for a hybrid approach - pure CFI thresholds fail because constant-format tokens (freq=160, CFI=1.0) are metaprogramming artifacts, not meaningful patterns. The concrete scoring formula is now defined: score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120).\n","name":"powershell Bypass"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774371398193}}
